author: Tom Brueggemann
title: ‘Moonfall’ and ‘Jackass Forever’ Can’t Dislodge ‘Spider-Man: No Way Home’ on VOD
description: At Netflix, Judd Apatow's "The Bubble" is #3, but Richard Linklater's "Apollo 10 1/2" fell short of the Top 10.
content: In its third week at #1, “Spider-Man: No Way Home” (Sony/$19.99) leads VOD charts at iTunes and Google Play (by transactions) and Vudu (by revenue). In more than 18 months of charting VOD play, it ti… [+5247 chars]
